  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Safe working in education, childcare and children’s social care
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Preventing and controlling infection, including the use of PPE, in education, childcare and children’s social care settings during the coronavirus outbreak.</p>

  </div>
</div>

